fields.value: Timing of the formation and migration of giant planets as constrained by CB chondrites

dsDescriptionValue.value: Files tracking collisions for various runs produced in the paper entitled "Timing of the formation and migration of giant planets as constrained by CB chondrites".

files.description: All collisions occurring tracked down to 2 km diameter bodies for the evoltion of the excited main belt disk with no gas. Columns are 1 - time (yr) 2 - particle id 3 - target radius (km) 4 - impactor radius (km) 5 - mass of target (Earth Mass) 6 - Mass of impactor (Earth Mass) 7 - impact velocity (km/s) 8,9,10 x,y,x, (AU) of target

files.description:
Collisions onto embryos with Grand Tack like planet migration at 2 Myr this file does not include impacts with jupiter.
Columns are
1 - run name
2 - time (yr)
3 - mass of body 1 (Earth masses)
4 - mass of body 2 (Earth masses)
5 - v_imp (km/s)
6 - v_imp / v_esc
7 - impact angle degrees
8 - is it and embryo-embryo impact 
      (1-yes 0-no)

5 - mass of target (Earth Mass)
